---
title: Mexican 'Un-Stuffed' Pepper Bowls with Black Beans
description: A veggie-full twist on mom's stuffed peppers, bursting with Mexican-inspired flavours! Green onion-spiked basmati and saucy black beans round out these bowls for a satisfying dinner.
